import re -> library for regular expression
import requests -> library that makes a request to a web page
from bs4 import BeautifulSoup -> library that makes it easy to scrape information from web pages
from flask import Flask, request -> this is a lightweight Python web framework that provides useful tools and features for creating web applications in the Python Language
import pymongo -> this is a Python distribution containing tools for working with MongoDB
import json -> this library is used to work with json